<div class="modal js-modal" id="callback">
    <div class="modal__inner">
        <button class="modal__close js-close-modal">
            <svg width="45" height="45" aria-hidden="true"
                 class="icon-cross">
                <use xlink:href="#cross"></use>
            </svg>
        </button>
        <h3 class="modal__heading">
            Оставьте ваши контакты
        </h3>
        <form action="/" method="POST" class="modal__form" data-need-validation="">
            <div class="modal__form-fields">
                <div class="modal__form-field">
                    <input type="text" class="modal__form-input" name="your-name" placeholder="Имя" required>
                </div>
                <div class="modal__form-field">
                    <input type="tel" class="modal__form-input js-phone-input" name="your-phone" placeholder="Телефон"
                           required data-parsley-phone="">
                </div>
                <div class="modal__form-field">
                    <input type="email" class="modal__form-input" name="your-email" placeholder="Почта" required>
                </div>
                <div class="modal__form-field">
                    <input type="text" class="modal__form-input" name="your-company" placeholder="Организация">
                </div>
                <div class="modal__form-field">
                    <textarea name="your-comment" class="modal__form-input" placeholder="Комментарий"></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="modal__form-submit" type="submit">
                Отправить
            </button>
            <div class="modal__form-policy">
                Нажимая на кнопку, я соглашаюсь с <a href="#">политикой конфиденциальности</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="modal js-modal" id="callback-success">
    <div class="modal__inner">
        <button class="modal__close js-close-modal">
            <svg width="45" height="45" aria-hidden="true"
                 class="icon-cross">
                <use xlink:href="#cross"></use>
            </svg>
        </button>
        <h3 class="modal__heading">
            Спасибо за обращение!
        </h3>
        <div class="modal__text">
            Пока наш специалист связывается с вами, почитайте полезный материал
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="modal__material">
            Как защитить свой товарный знак
            <svg width="45" height="45" aria-hidden="true"
                 class="icon-diagonal-arrow">
                <use xlink:href="#diagonal-arrow"></use>
            </svg>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>